<MainLayout>
	<h1>Learning in Public</h1>
	<p>
		here's where i'll be documenting my study on topica that i randomly get
		interested in! for example, there might be cybersec writeups for ctf's and
		such, or it might be sharing my notes on a certain math textbook. who knows?
	</p>
	<p>
